Responsibilities:

  Customer engagement and support
  Optimise sales opportunities
  Merchandise display and replenishment of stocks
  Assist with stock take
  Perform general housekeeping duties


Requirements:

  Minimum GCE ‘N’/ ‘O’ level with minimum 1-2 years of retail experience preferred
  Customer service oriented, pleasant disposition and meticulous

Working days and timing:


  5 days work week
  1 hour lunch break and 1 hour dinner break&nbsp;
  Must work retail hours including weekends and Public &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Holidays (exclude Chinese New Year)&nbsp;
